this position right now.

00:28.779 --> 00:30.406
I'm not the one who
put you in it.

00:30.489 --> 00:31.957
Jack Soloff is.

00:32.241 --> 00:34.494
This is your last
chance to work with me.

00:34.826 --> 00:36.544
Take it, and you
have a future.

00:36.620 --> 00:40.045
