01:45.439 --> 01:46.486
You poor thing.

01:48.525 --> 01:49.526
"You poor thing."

01:50.444 --> 01:51.445
That's what stuck with me.

01:52.195 --> 01:53.617
She said, "You poor thing."

01:53.697 --> 01:55.199
But she didn't give
a shit about me.

01:55.616 --> 01:56.742
And did you know
what you saw?

01:59.536 --> 02:01.709
No, I just knew
something was wrong.

02:02.372 --> 02:03.464
And you didn't
tell your father.

02:04.207 --> 02:05.208
She told me not to.

02:06.126 --> 02:07.127
And you trusted her.

02:07.878 --> 02:08.878
I did.

02:09.880 --> 02:12.554
Harvey, I never thought I'd be
saying this to you, but I'm proud.

02:13.592 --> 02:15.594
It took an amazing amount of
courage to tell me that.

02:15.719 --> 02:17.972
