note for once.

02:27.689 --> 02:29.362
The Peterson case, huh?

02:29.650 --> 02:31.402
I remember when I used to
handle that asshole.

02:31.568 --> 02:34.492
That's funny. I don't remember
inviting you into my office.

02:35.113 --> 02:36.114
Oh yeah, that's right.

02:36.198 --> 02:38.200
