02:50.212 --> 02:51.213
What the hell is this?

02:51.588 --> 02:54.341
A case that's tailor-made for someone
with a hedge fund background.

02:56.301 --> 02:58.099
New York teacher's
pension fund just lost

02:58.178 --> 02:59.771
30% of their
annual income.

03:00.055 --> 03:02.899
