03:43.390 --> 03:44.733
What? It's not my birthday.

03:45.225 --> 03:46.477
Oh, come on.
You can tell me.

03:46.560 --> 03:48.403
What is it, 48? 49?

03:48.478 --> 03:49.604
The big 6-0?

03:49.688 --> 03:51.736
A, I'm not the
one pushing 60.

03:51.815 --> 03:53.283
You better not be
talking to me.

03:53.358 --> 03:56.237
B, if it were, I'd be
drinking with someone a lot

03:56.319 --> 03:57.491
