03:57.988 --> 03:59.661
Then why is Wednesday
night permanently

03:59.740 --> 04:01.037
blocked out on
your calendar?

04:08.749 --> 04:10.217
Donna.
Harvey.

04:10.500 --> 04:11.467
You look busy.

04:11.543 --> 04:12.840
I look busy because I am busy.

04:15.130 --> 04:16.130
