04:17.132 --> 04:19.476
Too busy to join me at
Del Posto on Wednesday night?

04:21.636 --> 04:23.263
Harvey, we don't need
to do that anymore.

04:23.764 --> 04:26.392
Then why did you leave it permanently
blocked off on my calendar?

04:26.475 --> 04:27.977
