on decent terms?

04:43.283 --> 04:44.626
It's only been a
week and a half.

04:45.243 --> 04:46.244
Seriously, Donna.

04:47.996 --> 04:50.124
I don't just want to
be on decent terms.

04:50.207 --> 04:51.584
