to being friends.

04:51.666 --> 04:53.009
That's really nice, Harvey.

04:55.504 --> 04:56.505
See you Wednesday night.

05:02.010 --> 05:03.011
Thanks.

05:05.180 --> 05:06.227
Jessica!

05:07.140 --> 05:08.642
What a pleasant surprise.

05:08.725 --> 05:10.068
I think we both know
that it isn't.

05:10.477 --> 05:12.730
Pleasant, or a surprise? Either.

05:12.813 --> 05:14.656
