how to land a new client.

05:25.408 --> 05:26.660
He was so determined,

05:26.743 --> 05:29.622
I was suddenly reminded
of Harvey's first client.

05:29.704 --> 05:30.751
McKernon Motors.

05:30.831 --> 05:32.174
The client he cared
so much about,

05:32.249 --> 05:35.344
he gave up a promotion
just to keep his word.

05:35.752 --> 05:37.220
It's hard to forget
a move like that.

05:37.295 --> 05:40.048
