your house to damage it.

05:55.564 --> 05:57.362
You did that all by yourself

05:57.440 --> 05:58.987
the second you let
Fletcher Engines go.

05:59.067 --> 06:00.034
Jack tell you that?

06:00.110 --> 06:01.783
Fletcher Engines
told everyone that.

06:02.279 --> 06:03.531
And you told
your entire firm

06:03.613 --> 06:06.162
that you care more about Harvey
