06:59.252 --> 07:00.925
Oh, you're going to
deny that you've been

07:01.004 --> 07:02.347
spreading word
around the office

07:02.422 --> 07:03.799
that I told you to drop
Fletcher Engines?

07:04.174 --> 07:06.427
Yes. I'm gonna deny it,
because I didn't do it.

07:06.509 --> 07:08.261
Then how the hell
does everybody know?

07:08.345 --> 07:11.098
