look like shit.

07:16.311 --> 07:18.530
Well, it didn't make me come out
smelling like a rose either.

07:18.647 --> 07:20.320
And your mentor seems
to have known that.

07:20.398 --> 07:21.866
He's not my mentor.

07:21.942 --> 07:23.285
I went to him for advice

07:23.360 --> 07:25.488
and all it got me was
almost getting fired.

07:25.570 --> 07:27.493
But you said you'd give
me one more chance.

07:27.572 --> 07:29.040
And I've been trying
to take it.

07:29.115 --> 07:30.367
Give me one good
example of that.

07:30.450 --> 07:32.703
I approached Mike Ross to
work with me this morning.

07:32.786 --> 07:34.504
And by the way,
he spat in my face.

07:35.956 --> 07:37.003
