fire me anyway

07:45.298 --> 07:47.050
why give me the chance
in the first place?

07:49.719 --> 07:50.720
A joke?

07:50.804 --> 07:52.021
Uh, do you
hear me laughing?

07:52.514 --> 07:54.733
10% is 11%
more than you deserve.

07:54.808 --> 07:56.731
I'll... What the hell?

07:58.061 --> 07:59.062
