to close a deal.

08:00.230 --> 08:01.982
I just heard a rumor
that Jack Soloff

08:02.065 --> 08:03.191
signed Fletcher Engines.

08:03.775 --> 08:05.948
That's ridiculous. Everyone
knows we can't sign Fletcher

08:06.027 --> 08:06.994
if we represent McKernon.

08:07.070 --> 08:08.617
