to drop them.

08:12.367 --> 08:14.119
And the only reason Jack
would have done that

08:14.202 --> 08:16.625
in the first place is if you
were fired by McKernon.

08:17.914 --> 08:18.915
Harvey, I can explain.

08:18.999 --> 08:20.171
Goddamn it, I knew it.

08:20.250 --> 08:22.594
Just wait a minute.
Harvey, listen to me.

08:23.086 --> 08:24.303
Jack set us up.

08:24.629 --> 08:26.097
He acted as if he
was cooperating

08:26.172 --> 08:27.890
when all along he was
looking to blow up the deal.

08:27.966 --> 08:29.309
Why the hell didn't you come
to me when it happened?

08:29.384 --> 08:30.476
Because we wanted to
fix it ourselves.

08:30.552 --> 08:32.679
Wanting to fix it yourself
is the cause of every problem

08:32.761 --> 08:33.763
you and I have ever had.

08:33.847 --> 08:35.063
And now you're teaching
that bullshit to Mike?

08:35.472 --> 08:36.941
You know what? Mike and
I worked on that deal

08:37.017 --> 08:38.269
together and we kicked ass.

08:38.809 --> 08:41.107
I'm happy, Mike's happy,
Dominic's happy.

08:41.187 --> 08:42.438
And I'll tell you why.

08:42.647 --> 08:44.615
Because I'm a damn good
attorney and you know it.

08:44.941 --> 08:46.363
So, if that's the only
thing you came in here for,

08:46.443 --> 08:47.535
I would like to
close my deal now.

08:55.869 --> 08:58.167
Mr. Specter,
Esther Litt just called.

08:58.246 --> 09:00.374
She has an urgent matter,
needs to see you right away.

09:00.665 --> 09:02.588
Did she say what
it was about?

09:02.667 --> 09:04.340
Just not to
tell her brother.

09:10.592 --> 09:13.562
Oh, so this is where the little
people get their caffeine.

09:14.137 --> 09:16.606
I'm guessing you're not here
to have a breakfast bar.

09:17.015 --> 09:18.688
I've never had a
breakfast bar in my life.

09:19.476 --> 09:21.604
