ambitious attorney

09:48.046 --> 09:49.263
that ever took me on,

09:49.339 --> 09:51.512
there'd be nobody left here
but me and Harold Gunderson.

09:53.009 --> 09:54.852
Wait a second. You know who
Harold Gunderson is?

09:55.178 --> 09:56.350
I know who everybody is.

09:56.429 --> 09:58.181
And before you say
one more word,

09:58.264 --> 10:01.768
if I ever start handing out
pink slips for troublemakers...

10:01.851 --> 10:03.103
You'd be the first in line.

10:03.686 --> 10:04.687
Right.

10:07.065 --> 10:09.284
I came here as soon as
I got your message.

10:09.359 --> 10:11.032
I don't do that
for most people.

10:11.861 --> 10:13.078
So much for hard to get.

10:13.196 --> 10:14.243
I think we're past that.

10:14.864 --> 10:16.411
Did Jeffrey get
greedy again?

10:16.533 --> 10:18.535
No. A man named
Kenneth Jackson

10:18.618 --> 10:20.120
is claiming my
nut-free muffins

10:20.203 --> 10:21.625
put him in
anaphylactic shock.

10:22.038 --> 10:23.881
What happened?
Too much gluten?

10:24.040 --> 10:25.041
Not enough gluten?

10:25.125 --> 10:26.798
Harvey, this isn't funny.

10:26.876 --> 10:28.628
This is my company, and

10:28.711 --> 10:30.839
my entire brand is
based on quality.

10:31.005 --> 10:32.427
I'm sorry.
I'll take it seriously.

10:33.550 --> 10:34.722
Thank you.
Don't thank me.

10:34.801 --> 10:37.805
Thank Louis, because he's
gonna handle this case.

10:39.222 --> 10:40.940
What?
This is a business matter,

10:41.015 --> 10:43.143
not personal. And I'm not
stealing Louis' client.

10:43.226 --> 10:44.398
You're not stealing me.

10:44.477 --> 10:45.945
