my divorce.

10:46.855 --> 10:49.199
Are you gonna tell me that Louis
is a better lawyer than you?

10:49.274 --> 10:51.652
No, I'm gonna tell you that
he's a damn good lawyer,

10:51.734 --> 10:53.111
and he'd do anything
to protect you.

10:53.194 --> 10:54.320
That's not the point.

10:54.404 --> 10:56.372
I need this to
go away quietly.

10:56.447 --> 10:58.916
And Louis doesn't do
anything quietly.

10:59.242 --> 11:01.165
Then tell him that.
He never listens to me.

11:01.244 --> 11:03.087
Then get him to listen or
get another law firm.

11:03.163 --> 11:04.460
Because I'm not
taking this case.

11:05.874 --> 11:08.878
Harvey, I don't need
another firm.

11:09.586 --> 11:10.633
I need you.

11:11.337 --> 11:12.680
You know what I think?

11:12.755 --> 11:14.473
I think you wanna go
out with me again

11:14.549 --> 11:15.675
and you came to
me with this

11:15.758 --> 11:17.055
because you were
afraid to say it to me.

11:17.135 --> 11:18.182
I don't believe you!

11:18.261 --> 11:21.686
You think I concocted a lawsuit
against my own company

11:21.764 --> 11:24.438
