been with that I like him?

11:25.226 --> 11:26.273
Sure looks that way.

11:26.769 --> 11:30.364
In that case, I guess I do have
the wrong man for the job.

11:31.774 --> 11:33.242
Thank you for taking the time.

11:50.585 --> 11:51.962
Please let him
know I'm here.

11:52.629 --> 11:53.801
Esther.

11:55.340 --> 11:56.387
What are you doing here?

11:56.466 --> 11:58.264
I thought I was very
clear yesterday.

11:58.384 --> 12:00.478
I'm not taking your case.
You were clear.

12:01.012 --> 12:02.559
I'm here to see Louis.

12:03.264 --> 12:06.268
But it's nice to see your
ego is as strong as ever.

12:07.060 --> 12:08.232
I'm sorry.

12:08.311 --> 12:10.279
And I didn't mean to be
such a dick yesterday.

12:10.355 --> 12:11.402
It's okay, Harvey.

12:11.481 --> 12:12.482
I know what you did.

12:12.899 --> 12:14.901
You accused me of what
you accused me of

12:14.984 --> 12:16.110
so I would go to Louis.

12:16.194 --> 12:17.320
So, you're not
mad at me?

12:18.196 --> 12:20.073
It was actually sweet,

12:20.156 --> 12:22.158
in a dick-ish
sort of way.

12:23.076 --> 12:24.077
That's my specialty.

12:25.245 --> 12:26.337
Thanks, Harvey.

12:28.539 --> 12:30.507
Hi, Esther, I'm
Donna Paulsen.

12:30.583 --> 12:32.176
I'm Louis'...
I know who you are.

12:32.543 --> 12:34.511
You're the best thing that's
ever happened to my brother.

12:34.587 --> 12:36.806
Oh. Well, you don't
know the half of it.

12:38.841 --> 12:42.061
Anyway, I hope I didn't put you to
too much trouble on short notice.

12:42.178 --> 12:43.179
Oh, nonsense.

12:43.263 --> 12:45.061
Louis was thrilled when he
heard you were coming in.

12:45.139 --> 12:47.437
